  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-8 clean: bounded applicability)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package is a negative-control specimen for weakener NC-8: it explicitly declares both hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope with concrete numeric bounds, and demonstrates that the validation campaign densely covers the declared envelope. All 13 credibility factors are assessed with achievedLevel >= requiredLevel. Decision: Accepted.",
