      "rationale": "Simulation workflow documented in a controlled simulation plan reviewed by two independent subject matter experts. Boundary condition setup, mesh generation parameters, and post-processing scripts version-controlled and peer-reviewed. Blind replication study conducted by independent analyst produced results within 1.2% of primary analyst results for NIH at all 5 primary operating points.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/use-error-peer-review-report-2025"
